a": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661862920"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2vDC2buk24sNEAMaCTEwOTM1ODUxMCDLwd60BjAAOCNABnIJNjYxODYyOTIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1721654570.311494", "card_id": "Q_271267154", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "那些自命不凡的人 后来都怎样了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我就是好奇。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-ca2be30183254f44025481002f94b115_1440w.gif"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/271267154"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2vDC2buk24sNEAMaCDIyNTU2NjEzILyCnNYFMAA4iQFAB3IJMjcxMjY3MTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1721654570.312013", "card_id": "Q_661836585", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 2D 电子游戏会大量存在受击无敌、受击保护这种设定？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近通关了某个银河城游戏，发现网友的许多批评都集中在「游戏没有受击保护」这一点上。我仔细想了想，似乎在银河城游戏，横板过关游戏等等类型中，确实大部分游戏都有「角色受到伤害之后一段时间内无敌」这样的设定。但这是为什么？毕竟 3D 游戏中就几乎不存在这种设定。 我个人的理解是，相比于 3D 游戏，2D 游戏相对更强调玩家在有限的 2D 空间内精确运动，因此早期 2D 游戏通常会引入碰撞伤害这类设定以逼迫玩家在空间里动起来。而在这种情况下，如果不加入受击保护的话，主角很有可能会被连续的碰撞伤害直接多次判定给秒杀。 且 2D 游戏或多或少会存在一些平台跳跃要素，一旦玩家跌入陷阱，那就需要重置位置和摄像机，而在重制之后如果没有受击保护，那就容易出现「跌入陷阱 - 重置 - 挨打 - 跌入陷阱 -…」这样的循环。 问题抛砖引玉，看看各位的理解"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661836585"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2vDC2buk24sNEAMaCTEwOTM1MjY2OCC5t920BjAAOBJACHIJNjYxODM2NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1721654570.312814", "card_id": "Q_662022920", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 2024 年 7 月 22 日 A 股市场行情走势？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "下周会变盘吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f6077d3d3ab97cad8984db423958aec2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662022920"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2vDC2buk24sNEAMaCTEwOTM5NDA4MCCytui0BjAAOC1ACXIJNjYyMDIyOTIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1721654570.313105", "card_id": "Q_661920339", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "能提一首你认为最能表达暑热的诗词吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "找出诗词，解释诗词如何表达热"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c6f36cca7009f91d944168e6d5367f58_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_are